data.description: Two story brick in a tucked away sought after neighborhood.  Foyer with wainscoting upon entry shows off the refinished hardwood floors, in 2022.  Exquisite living room with wood burning fireplace. Oversized dining room for entertaining. Large eat-in kitchen with cabinets and pantry for any chef.  Large den with views of wooded backyard, second fireplace, along with a separate front porch entrance. Huge laundry room with stairs to the FROG. Large bedroom downstairs and separate full bath and 3 more bedrooms upstairs. The primary has 4 closets, nursery/dressing area and full bath.  3 attics with 4 walk in accesses. Near base, interstate and shopping.
